title: Projects
p1-descriptor: YearOne Ratings is a dynamic single-page application built with React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS, enabling users to search and rate movies seamlessly. Powered by the OMDB API, it provides real-time movie data, while Vercel ensures fast and reliable deployment. Designed for an intuitive user experience, YearOne Ratings offers a sleek and responsive interface for film enthusiasts.
p1-stack: React, JavaScript, CSS, HTML, OMDB API, Vercel
p2-descriptor: The Shoppies is a sleek, single-page application built with React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS, allowing users to search for movies and nominate their top five favorites. Leveraging the OMDB API for real-time movie data and deployed on Vercel for fast performance, The Shoppies delivers a smooth and engaging user experience for film enthusiasts.
p2-stack: React, JavaScript, CSS, HTML, OMDB API, Vercel
p3-descriptor: Wanderlust is a user-friendly web application designed for travelers to book rentals and connect with fellow adventurers. Built with React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS, it offers a seamless booking experience with a sleek interface. Deployed on Vercel for optimal performance, Wanderlust simplifies travel planning by fostering a community-driven rental experience.
p3-stack: React, JavaScript, CSS, HTML, OMDB API, Vercel
p4-descriptor: LaLaLime is a modern e-commerce platform specializing in athletic apparel, offering a seamless shopping experience. Built with React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS, it features a sleek UI and smooth navigation. Deployed on Vercel for fast and reliable performance, LaLaLime delivers a dynamic and responsive online retail experience for fitness enthusiasts.
p4-stack: React, JavaScript, CSS, HTML, OMDB API, Vercel
